<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-100 to-blue-300 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">

  
  <div class="max-w-6xl w-full grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between">

     
      <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6">
       <img src="/static/waterslip.jpeg" alt="water drop image" class="w-full h-auto">
      </div>

      
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4 text-center">
        Daily Drip
      </h1>

      
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Welcome to Daily Drip — your simple, smart hydration companion.
        We help you calculate exactly how much water your body needs
        and make it easier to build healthy habits every single day.
      </p>

 <div class="rounded-3xl  mb-6">
      <img src="/static/banner3.jpeg" alt="water banner" class="w-full h-auto">
      </div>


      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Many people walk around mildly dehydrated without realizing it.
        Low energy, headaches, brain fog, and mood changes can all
        be signs you’re not drinking enough water.          
        Waterly helps you stay consistent — one cup at a time.
      </p>

      
      <div class="rounded-3xl  mb-6">
      <img src="/static/banner4.png" alt="water banner" class="w-full h-auto">
      </div>

      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-3 text-center">
        ABOUT Daily Drip
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center leading-relaxed">
        We believe health should be simple.
        Waterly asks you easy questions about your age, weight,
        activity level, and lifestyle to calculate your personalized
        daily water goal — rounded to the nearest cup.
      </p>

    </div>


    <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col">

     
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 text-center mb-2">
        PERSONALIZED HYDRATION
      </h2>

      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-8">
        Calculate • Track • Improve
      </p>

    
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-4 text-center">
          <img src="/static/calculator.jpeg" alt="calculator image"> 
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mt-3">
            Smart Calculation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Get your custom daily water goal based on your body and lifestyle.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-4 text-center">
          <img src="/static/tracking.jpeg" alt="water tracking app image">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mt-3">
            Daily Tracking
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Log each cup and see your progress in real time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-4 text-center leading-relaxed">
          <img src="/static/summerdrinks!.jpeg" alt="friends drinking water image">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mt-3">
            Play with Friends
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            challenge your friends to see who can stay more hydrated each week!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-4 text-center">
          <img src="/static/cutewater.jpeg" alt="people drinking water image">

          <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mt-3">
            Goal Motivation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Stay consistent with simple, realistic hydration goals.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      
      <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-3xl p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-gray-700  text-center">
          Your body is made up of about 60% water. That means hydration
          affects your energy, focus, muscle recovery, digestion,
          skin health, and overall mood. When you drink enough water,
          you think clearer, feel stronger, and perform better.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700  text-center mt-4">
          Waterly was built for students, athletes, busy adults,
          and anyone who wants to improve their health without
          complicated systems. No overwhelming features.
          Just simple, effective hydration tracking.
        </p>
      </div>

     
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-auto">

        <a href="/login"
           class="bg-white border-2 border-blue-500 text-blue-500 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white transition">
          Log In
        </a>

        <a href="/register"
           class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-600 transition">
          Register
        </a>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
